query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('magento-1.7',
'magento-1.9',
'magento2',
'module',
'php',
'product')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('magento')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10 group by t1.name;
